## Quick commands

```bash
uv sync --group dev
uv run pytest tests/ -v
uv run ruff check . && uv run ruff format .

databricks bundle deploy --target dev
# dev_id required for bundle run (job context); any unique string. Interactive notebooks omit it → current_user().
databricks bundle run integration_test_job --target dev --params dev_id=my_run,scenario=basic
databricks bundle run {{.project_name}}_pipeline --target dev --params dev_id=my_run
```

Set `owner` and `repository` in `cog.toml`, and `defaults.source_catalog` / `defaults.source_schema` in `config/app.yaml`, before relying on releases or non-dev environments.
